title: An Application Failed toInstall on My Phone, Why?
answer:
The possible causes are as follows：  
1、The APK you are trying to install is defective.  
2、The version of the APK you are trying to install is not compatible with Android 2.2 or the screen of your phone does not meet the screen specifications required by the APK.  
3、You are trying to install an application that is already installed on your phone. To install the application again, you must uninstall it first.  
4、There is insufficient phone memory for the application.
